    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Sliders with multiple values are not yet supported, but we might be able to fake it by using two sliders positionned on top of each other\n\nhttp://ng-range-slider.herokuapp.com/ (this example uses Angular, but I don't know to which extent yet)\n\nI still don't know how we could approach this one without relying on external dependencies, but I guess having our default markup as simple as possible (like real input form elements) is a good start.\n",
